snippet.title: Fisher-Price Time to Play Pet Shop Full Playthrough
snippet.description:
Fisher-Price Time to Play Pet Shop Full Playthrough

Fisher-Price Time to Play Pet Shop is a game created by Knowledge Adventure/Davidson Associates Inc. in 1996. In this game, children get to decorate their own pet shop by ordering what kind of pets they want, feed them, take care, and grooming their pets etc.
